                        <div class="div-full breadcrumb">    <div class="sitename">        <p class="sitename-name">Safety</p>        <p class="sitename-class">National Program</p>    </div>    <div class="location">        <h1 class='location-pagetitle'>How to Avoid Getting Caught in a Rip Current</h1>        <div class='location-breadcrumb'>            <a href="https://www.weather.gov">Weather.gov</a> &gt; <a href="https://www.weather.gov/safety">Safety</a> &gt; How to Avoid Getting Caught in a Rip Current        </div>    </div></div>
                        
                        
                        
